                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "American silver production had significantly increased, thereby lowering its price."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "The reduced availability of silver had made it costlier than ever before."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "Gold was more abundant than silver in most European nations."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_4",
                  "content": "European nations wanted to challenge the gold-oriented northern states."
